{"product_id":"honeysticks-beeswax-crayons-jumbos-16pk","title":"Honeysticks Beeswax Crayons Jumbos 16pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW184690971 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW184690971 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor little artists ready to grow their drawing and writing skills, \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Beeswax Crayons Jumbos 16pk\u003c\/strong\u003e offer more length, control, and creative potential. These Jumbo-sized crayons are designed for little hands with a more developed pencil grip, making them perfect for finer art colouring and detailed projects.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDesigned for growing grips:\u003c\/strong\u003e At 10cm long and 1.19cm thick, Honeysticks Jumbos offer just the right balance of length and control for confident young artists aged 3+.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBright, bold colour: \u003c\/strong\u003eMade with 100% pure New Zealand beeswax and food-grade colourants – no nasties, no fillers.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDurable and safe: \u003c\/strong\u003eTough enough to withstand serious colouring while staying safe and non-toxic.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eGreat for skill building:\u003c\/strong\u003e Encourages pencil-style grip, creative control, and artistic expression.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families: \u003c\/strong\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Jumbos are lovingly handmade in New Zealand to encourage creative expression from the very first scribble. \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":57531702772093,"sku":"HCRJM16","price":19.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/CJ16.png?v=1765230533","url":"https:\/\/honeysticks.co.uk\/products\/honeysticks-beeswax-crayons-jumbos-16pk","provider":"Honeysticks UK","version":"1.0","type":"link"}